  </div>

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">UK in JAPAN 2019-20 activity was halted briefly for a few months due to the COVID-19 pandemic. The campaign has restarted as UK in JAPAN in Sept 20. </p>

  </div>
</div>

